---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Title from "../components/Title.astro";
---

<html lang="es">
    <head>
        <BaseHead
            title="Dónde Encontrarnos - El Sablón"
            description="Visítanos en los mercados artesanales de Asturias"
        />
    </head>
    <body class="bg-surface-low">
        <main>
            <Header />

            <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto pt-16 pb-8 px-6 text-center">
                <Title title="Dónde Encontrarnos">
                    Cada mes nos instalamos en diferentes mercados artesanales
                    de Asturias. Ven a vernos, toca nuestros productos, conoce
                    el proceso artesanal y descubre piezas únicas hechas a mano.
                </Title>
            </section>

            <!-- Calendario Visual -->
            <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mb-10">
                <div class="bg-cream p-8 rounded-2xl shadow">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-title font-bold text-walnut-deep mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather">
                            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/>
                            <line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/>
                            <line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/>
                            <line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/>
                        </svg>
                        Calendario de Mercados
                    </h2>

                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
                        <!-- Primer domingo -->
                        <div class="bg-surface-low p-6 rounded-2xl border border-terra-cotta/20">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                                <div class="bg-terra-cotta text-cream w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                                    <span class="text-xs leading-none">1er</span>
                                    <span class="text-xl leading-tight">D</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Primer Domingo</p>
                                    <p class="text-2xl font-title font-bold text-walnut-deep">Oviñana</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed">
                                Un mercado familiar en pleno corazón de Asturias, perfecto para
                                disfrutar de la mañana con productos locales y artesanía
                                tradicional, con unas vistas impresionantes a la costa asturiana.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <!-- Tercer domingo -->
                        <div class="bg-surface-low p-6 rounded-2xl border border-moss-green/20">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
                                <div class="bg-moss-green text-cream w-14 h-14 rounded-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                                    <span class="text-xs leading-none">3er</span>
                                    <span class="text-xl leading-tight">D</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Tercer Domingo</p>
                                    <p class="text-2xl font-title font-bold text-walnut-deep">Somao</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-dark-brown/70 leading-relaxed">
                                El encanto de un pueblo asturiano repleto de casas de indianos,
                                premiado como Pueblo Ejemplar de Asturias. Artesanos, productores
                                locales y música en directo.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Horario -->
                    <div class="mt-5 bg-surface-low p-5 rounded-xl flex items-center gap-3">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0">
                            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
                        </svg>
                        <div>
                            <span class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Horario: </span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-dark-brown/70">Normalmente de 11:00h a 15:00h</span>
                            <span class="text-xs text-dark-brown/50 ml-2">— Confirma siempre en nuestras redes sociales</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Ubicaciones Detalladas -->
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 mb-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-7">
                <!-- Oviñana -->
                <article class="bg-cream rounded-2xl shadow overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="bg-terra-cotta p-6 text-cream">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-title font-bold mb-1">Oviñana</h2>
                        <p class="text-cream/80 text-sm">Primer domingo de cada mes</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6">
                        <img
                            src="/plaza_ovinana.webp"
                            alt="Plaza de Oviñana"
                            class="w-full h-56 object-cover rounded-xl shadow mb-6"
                        />

                        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Ubicación</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70">Plaza principal de Oviñana</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/>
                                    <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Ambiente</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70">
                                        Mercado artesanal con productos locales y ambiente muy
                                        familiar. Perfecto para toda la familia.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    <polygon points="3 11 22 2 13 21 11 13 3 11"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Cómo llegar</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70">
                                        Aparcamiento gratuito cerca de la plaza. Bien comunicado por carretera.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <a
                                href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Plaza+de+Oviñana,+33156+Oviñana,+Asturias"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-terra-cotta hover:bg-terra-cotta/85 text-cream py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-colors duration-200"
                            >
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                                </svg>
                                Ver en Google Maps
                            </a>

                            <iframe
                                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2922.393314583816!2d-6.237123684528927!3d43.56922197912327!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd36f7e7e6b2b8e1%3A0x7e2e6e6e6e6e6e6e!2sPlaza%20de%20Ovi%C3%B1ana%2C%2033156%20Ovi%C3%B1ana%2C%20Asturias!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1686754321000!5m2!1ses!2ses"
                                width="100%"
                                height="240"
                                style="border:0;"
                                allowfullscreen=""
                                loading="lazy"
                                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
                                class="rounded-xl mt-3"></iframe>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <!-- Somao -->
                <article class="bg-cream rounded-2xl shadow overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="bg-moss-green p-6 text-cream">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl font-title font-bold mb-1">Somao</h2>
                        <p class="text-cream/80 text-sm">Tercer domingo de cada mes</p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6">
                        <img
                            src="/plaza_somao.webp"
                            alt="Plaza de Somao"
                            class="w-full h-56 object-cover rounded-xl shadow mb-6"
                        />

                        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Ubicación</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70">Plaza principal de Somao</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"/>
                                    <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Ambiente</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70">
                                        Mercado acogedor en un pueblo con encanto. Artesanos
                                        locales, productores de la zona y música en vivo.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-leather flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    <polygon points="3 11 22 2 13 21 11 13 3 11"/>
                                </svg>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-semibold text-walnut-deep text-sm">Cómo llegar</p>
                                    <p class="text-xs text-dark-brown/70">
                                        Fácil acceso desde Gijón y Avilés. Parking disponible en el pueblo.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <a
                                href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Somao,+33139,+Asturias"
                                target="_blank"
                                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full bg-moss-green hover:bg-moss-green/85 text-cream py-3 rounded-full font-semibold text-sm transition-colors duration-200"
                            >
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/>
                                    <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                                </svg>
                                Ver en Google Maps
                            </a>

                            <iframe
                                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2923.036457769463!2d-6.181370684529326!3d43.5816249791227!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd36f7e2b7e6b8e1%3A0x7e2e6e6e6e6e6e6e!2sSomao%2C%2033139%20Pravia%2C%20Asturias!5e0!3m2!1ses!2ses!4v1686754321001!5m2!1ses!2ses"
                                width="100%"
                                height="240"
                                style="border:0;"
                                allowfullscreen=""
                                loading="lazy"
                                referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
                                class="rounded-xl mt-3"></iframe>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 mb-16">
                <div class="bg-leather text-cream p-10 md:p-12 rounded-2xl text-center">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-title font-bold mb-3">
                        ¿No puedes venir al mercado?
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg mb-7 text-cream/85 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                        Contacta con nosotros para coordinar una visita al taller
                        o consultar disponibilidad de productos.
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="/contacto"
                        class="inline-block bg-cream text-leather px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-wood-light transition-colors duration-200"
                    >
                        Contáctanos
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>

            <Footer />
        </main>
    </body>
</html>
